      "role": "user",
      "content": "closure is a weird word for it. it doesn't feel like a waypoint or a new chapter. it feels more like the end of the itinerary. like, when u finish the tour and the guide just stops talking and everyone goes home. i'm just tired of the constant movement and trying to find meaning in every view. i feel like i've reached the end of my track.",
